0this%20new%20medium.%3Cbr%3E%0A%3Cbr%3E%0A%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A13.5pt%22%3EBill%20Clinton%20Wants%20to%20Put%20%22Big%0ABrother%22%20in%20Your%20Computer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%0ABill%20Clinton%20believes%20in%20bureaucratic%20micro-management%20of%20the%20information%0Aeconomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cul%20type%3D%22disc%22%3E%0A%20%3Cli%20class%3D%22MsoNormal%22%20style%3D%22mso-margin-top-alt%3Aauto%3Bmso-margin-bottom-alt%3Aauto%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20mso-list%3Al11%20level1%20lfo21%3Btab-stops%3Alist%20.5in%22%3EWithin%20his%20first%20100%20days%0A%20%20%20%20%20as%20President%2C%20Bill%20Clinton%20proposed%20the%20Clipper%20Chip%20--%20a%20secret%0A%20%20%20%20%20government-controlled%20encryption%20algorithm%20--%20and%20a%20companion%20key%20escrow%0A%20%20%20%20%20system%20where%20two%20government%20agencies%20would%20hold%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20keys%20for%20every%0A%20%20%20%20%20Clipper%20user.%20Since%20then%20Bill%20Clinton%20has%20released%20updated%20versions%20of%0A%20%20%20%20%20encryption%20proposals%20which%20insist%20that%20the%20government%20hold%20a%20key%20to%0A%20%20%20%20%20individual's%20private%20data%20communications.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%3Cli%20class%3D%22MsoNormal%22%20style%3D%22mso-margin-top-alt%3Aauto%3Bmargin-bottom%3A12.0pt%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20mso-list%3Al11%20level1%20lfo21%3Btab-stops%3Alist%20.5in%22%3EThe%20Clinton%0A%20%20%20%20%20Administration's%20Internet%20Task%20Force%20has%20proposed%20legislation%20that%20would%0A%20%20%20%20%20reduce%20the%20rights%20of%20users%20of%20copyrighted%20material%20if%20that%20information%20is%0A%20%20%20%20%20used%20on%20the%20Internet.%20Their%20infamous%20%22NII%20White%20Paper%22%20ignored%0A%20%20%20%20%20important%20court%20decisions%20which%20balance%20the%20rights%20of%20information%20users%0A%20%20%20%20%20with%20those%20of%20information%20creators.%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A13.5pt%22%3EBob%20Dole%20Will%20Protect%20the%20Constitutional%0A%20%20%20%20%20Liberty%20of%20Internet%20Users%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20Bob%20Dole%20is%20concerned%20about%20children%20accessing%20unsuitable%20material%20when%0A%20%20%20%20%20using%20the%20Internet.%20But%20strict%20censorship%20of%20the%20Internet%20is%20not%20the%0A%20%20%20%20%20answer.%20Bob%20Dole%20believes%20that%20parents%20should%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%0A%20%20%20%20%20material%20that%20their%20children%20view%2C%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20encourage%20technology%0A%20%20%20%20%20which%20allows%20those%20decisions%20to%20be%20made%20within%20each%20home.%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20Throughout%20his%20Senate%20career%2C%20Bob%20Dole%20has%20fought%20to%20protect%20the%0A%20%20%20%20%20Constitutional%20liberty%20of%20Americans%3A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%3Cli%20class%3D%22MsoNormal%22%20style%3D%22mso-margin-top-alt%3Aauto%3Bmso-margin-bottom-alt%3Aauto%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20mso-list%3Al11%20level1%20lfo21%3Btab-stops%3Alist%20.5in%22%3EBob%20Dole%20is%20a%20supporter%20of%0A%20%20%20%20%20the%20Pro-CODE%20bill%20that%20limits%20the%20federal%20government's%20control%20of%0A%20%20%20%20%20encryption%20and%20user%20keys.%20It%20permits%20the%20export%20of%20software%20that%20includes%0A%20%20%20%20%20encryption%20if%20the%20software%20is%20easily%20available%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%3Cli%20class%3D%22MsoNormal%22%20style%3D%22mso-margin-top-alt%3Aauto%3Bmso-margin-bottom-alt%3Aauto%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20mso-list%3Al11%20level1%20lfo21%3Btab-stops%3Alist%20.5in%22%3EBob%20Dole%20strongly%20supports%0A%20%20%20%20%20the%20observations%20made%20in%20the%20recent%20National%20Research%20Council%20report%20that%0A%20%20%20%20%20widespread%20use%20of%20encryption%20to%20promote%20information%20security%20outweighs%20the%0A%20%20%20%20%20difficulties%20encrypted%20communications%20place%20on%20law%20enforcement.%20Economic%0A%20%20%20%20%20espionage%20from%20foreign%